- added Unit.AddProcHandler(ProcHandlerTemplate)
- example to trigger a spell every second time a negative action is performed on myNPC:
static readonly ProcHandlerTemplate spellTrigger = new TriggerSpellProcHandlerTemplate(ProcTriggerFlags.AnyHit, SpellHandler.GetSpell(SpellId.MySpell), 50);
// ...
 myNPC.AddProcHandler(spellTrigger);